    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">场景：API网关需要统一鉴权、限流、日志
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">云厂商方案：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── 阿里云API网关
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── 插件：JWT鉴权、流量控制、参数校验
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── 后端：直接路由到VPC内的ECS/容器
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└── AWS API Gateway + Lambda Authorizer
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ├── Lambda函数做自定义鉴权逻辑
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    └── 集成WAF做防护
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">自研 vs 托管权衡：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 托管网关：配置即使用，运维成本低
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 自研网关（如Spring Cloud Gateway）：灵活度高，但需要自己维护高可用</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="图片缩略图处理方案">图片缩略图处理方案</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>方案</th>
          <th>实现</th>
          <th>适用场景</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>实时处理</td>
          <td>上传原图 → 请求时按参数实时生成缩略图</td>
          <td>图片量小、规格多变</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>预生成</td>
          <td>上传时生成多规格缩略图</td>
          <td>图片量大、规格固定</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>云厂商托管</td>
          <td>OSS + 图片处理服务（IMG）</td>
          <td>不想自建处理集群</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
